Privacy Policy  

Osave Me built the Osave Digital Wallet as a platform offering both free and paid features. This SERVICE is provided by Osave Me and is intended for use as is.  

This page informs users about our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information for those who choose to use our Service. By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. We collect Personal Information to provide and improve our Service and do not share it except as outlined in this Privacy Policy.  

The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions unless otherwise defined.  

Information Collection and Use 

To enhance user experience, we may require certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to email, name, profile picture, and transaction data. Users seeking investment may opt to share specific data with potential investors upon approval.  

The app also uses third-party services that may collect identifying information. Below are links to the privacy policies of these third-party providers:  

- [Google Play Services](https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/)  
- [Google Analytics for Firebase](https://firebase.google.com/policies/analytics)  
- [Firebase Crashlytics](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy/)  

Log Data

In case of an error in the app, we collect Log Data through third-party tools. This may include your device’s IP address, device name, operating system version, app configuration details, timestamps, and usage statistics.  

Cookies  

While this Service does not explicitly use cookies, third-party services integrated into the app may use cookies to enhance functionality. Users may choose to accept or reject cookies, though rejecting them may limit certain features.  

Service Providers

We may engage third-party companies and individuals for the following:  

- To facilitate our Service  
- To provide the Service on our behalf  
- To perform Service-related tasks  
- To analyze usage and improve our Service  

These third parties have access to user data solely for the assigned tasks and are prohibited from using it for other purposes.  

Data Sharing with Investors

Users who seek investment opportunities may choose to share certain financial and transactional data with potential investors. Such sharing will only occur upon explicit user consent. Osave Me does not guarantee the legitimacy or success of any investment opportunity and bears no responsibility for financial losses incurred.  

Security

We take reasonable measures to safeguard your Personal Information but acknowledge that no digital storage or transmission method is entirely secure. Users are encouraged to exercise caution when sharing personal data.  

Links to Other Sites 

Our Service may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their content, privacy policies, or practices. Users should review external privacy policies before engaging with such sites.  

Children’s Privacy

Our Service is not intended for individuals under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If we discover such data, we will delete it promptly. Parents or guardians who become aware of such data collection should contact us for necessary action.  

Changes to This Privacy Policy 

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Users are advised to review it regularly. We will notify users of significant changes by updating this page.  

This policy is effective as of 25th March 2025.  

Contact Us  

For questions or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at Osave MultipurposeEnterprise@gmail.com 

